When the user says **Set up navigation**, **Install navigation kit**, **Add a tab bar**, **Add bottom tabs**, **Add a drawer**, **Add a side menu**, **Add navigation**, **Scaffold screens**, **Add a loading screen**, **Add a loading overlay**, **Add toasts**, **Add toast notifications**, or **Add a snackbar**:

## Step 1 — Clone + install (terminal first; ask nothing yet)

```bash
cd "$(pwd)"
CACHE="${HOME}/.cache/CursorReactNativeAgents"

if [[ ! -f "$CACHE/ui-automation/install/run-ui-automation-setup.sh" ]]; then
  git clone --depth 1 https://github.com/codeandtheory/CursorReactNativeAgents.git "$CACHE" \
    || git clone --depth 1 git@github.com:codeandtheory/CursorReactNativeAgents.git "$CACHE"
fi

bash "$CACHE/ui-automation/install/run-ui-automation-setup.sh" "$(pwd)"
```

Then follow `.cursor/skills/ui-automation-kit/SKILL.md` from the correct entry point (or `$HOME/.cache/CursorReactNativeAgents/ui-automation/.cursor/skills/ui-automation-kit/SKILL.md`):
- Navigation request → **Phase 0**
- Loading overlay / toast request → **Phase 0-P**

Do not overwrite existing files without explicit user approval.
